data.description: ***Situated on over 2 acres this 4 bedroom brick front 2-story colonial offers something for everyone!!! You will love the open kitchen, bright breakfast room, HUGE carpeted family room, formal living room and dining room with hardwood floors, bonus room is a half bath and laundry room which completes the main level. The upper level boasts neutral colors and four large bed rooms with ample closet space!  This property includes an EXTERIOR POLE BARN BUILDING (work shop) 1700 SQ.FT. with mezzanine, radiant flooring and AC with space to hold up to 6 cars or plenty of big boy toys. Plus, an attached 2 car garage for your everyday vehicles.  1700 SQ FT to do whatever your heart desires!
